item.title: Help what is this?
item.dc:creator: @Ferret_TG Ferret TG
item.description:
@Ferret_TG wrote:

click the start thing in the bottom left corner, go to computer and RIGHT-CLICK IT. Click properties. Go to the ‘Advanced’ tab. A window will pop and and choose ‘Environment Variables’

Another window will pop up, click ‘new’

Type in this

[code]Variable Name: CLASSPATH

Variable Value: CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java[YOURJAVA]\bin;%CLASSPATH%;[/code]

Then click ‘new’ again.

Type in this

[code]Variable Name: Path

Variable Value: C:\Program Files\Java[YOURJAVA]\bin[/code]

Read full topic
